OL,3,C'I feel like a second class citizen' -
OL,4,Cguide dog user speaks out after taxi
OL,5,Csnub
OL,7,FBy Tom Taylor
OL,9,FIt's against the law for taxi drivers
OL,10,Fto refuse access to guide dog owners -
OL,11,Fbut that message isn't getting
OL,12,Fthrough, according to charity Guide
OL,13,FDogs Cymru.
OL,15,FGuide dog owner Ryan Moreland told ITV
OL,16,FNews that refusals happen "more often
OL,17,Fthan I care to admit" when taxi
OL,18,Fdrivers see his companion Jamie.
