OL,3,C'I feel like a second class citizen' -
OL,4,Cguide dog user speaks out after taxi
OL,5,Csnub
OL,7,F"(I feel) almost like a second-class
OL,8,Fcitizen - like I'm not as worthy of a
OL,9,Fservice than someone else because I
OL,10,Fhave a dog.
OL,12,F"I've had, at the other end, instances
OL,13,Fof being charged extra for the
OL,14,Fprivilege and then been made to feel
OL,15,Funcomfortable in the journey which
OL,16,Fmakes me a bit frightened to use taxis
OL,17,Fin the future."
