OL,3,C'I feel like a second class citizen' -
OL,4,Cguide dog user speaks out after taxi
OL,5,Csnub
OL,7,FRyan decided to speak out about the
OL,8,Fissue after a recent incident with
OL,9,Ftaxi firm Veezu in Cardiff which made
OL,10,Fhim late for a hospital appointment.
OL,12,F"The one taxi, he drove past. I could
OL,13,Fsee him on the app go to the far end
OL,14,Fof my estate and then the job changed
OL,15,Fto 'searching for available drivers'
OL,16,Fwhich is a very common thing that I've
OL,17,Fexperienced where they don't want to
OL,18,Ftake the dog."
