OL,3,C'I feel like a second class citizen' -
OL,4,Cguide dog user speaks out after taxi
OL,5,Csnub
OL,7,FRyan then had to wait for another
OL,8,Fdriver to arrive from Veezu to take
OL,9,Fhim to his appointment which he was
OL,10,Fthen 15 minutes late for.
OL,12,FVeezu said it had reported the
OL,13,Fincident to the local licensing
OL,14,Fauthority, adding:
OL,16,F"Driver partners operating via Veezu
OL,17,Fare self-employed individuals and as
OL,18,Fsuch are responsible for their own
OL,19,Factions.
