OL,3,C'I feel like a second class citizen' -
OL,4,Cguide dog user speaks out after taxi
OL,5,Csnub
OL,7,F"As a licensed operator, we have
OL,8,Freported this matter to the Local
OL,9,FLicensing Authority for investigation
OL,10,Fand deactivated the driver partner
OL,11,Faccess to the Veezu booking system.
OL,13,F"We do not tolerate discrimination and
OL,14,Ftake incidents like this very
OL,15,Fseriously. We will continue to work
OL,16,Fwith the local licensing authorities
OL,17,Fand passenger groups to raise
OL,18,Fawareness and eliminate cases like
OL,19,Fthis."
