OL,3,C'I feel like a second class citizen' -
OL,4,Cguide dog user speaks out after taxi
OL,5,Csnub
OL,7,FA survey carried out by Guide Dogs in
OL,8,F2022 found that 63% of respondents
OL,9,Fsaid they had been refused access to
OL,10,Ftaxi or private hire vehicles in a 12-
OL,11,Fmonth period.
OL,13,FKerry Bevan, Head of Service at the
OL,14,Fcharity said: "It's a criminal offence
OL,15,Fto refuse access to a guide dog and
OL,16,Falso to charge extra to carry the dog.
