OL,3,C'I feel like a second class citizen' -
OL,4,Cguide dog user speaks out after taxi
OL,5,Csnub
OL,7,F"Some guide dogs moult, especially
OL,8,Fwith the seasons, so (the drivers) are
OL,9,Fthinking they've got to clean their
OL,10,Fcar after, which in my experience
OL,11,Fisn't really a valid excuse because it
OL,12,Ftakes two minutes to hoover if there
OL,13,Fis an issue. Most guide dogs are as
OL,14,Fgood as gold."
OL,16,FLast year a Welsh Government white
OL,17,Fpaper proposed national standards and
OL,18,Ftraining for all drivers.
OL,20,FIn a statement, the Welsh Government
OL,21,Fsaid:
