OL,3,C'I feel like a second class citizen' -
OL,4,Cguide dog user speaks out after taxi
OL,5,Csnub
OL,7,F"It is illegal for taxi drivers to
OL,8,Frefuse access to guide dog users and
OL,9,Ftheir dogs. Those that are refused
OL,10,Faccess to taxis and private hire
OL,11,Fvehicles should complain to their
OL,12,Flocal authority.
OL,14,F"Last year, we consulted on plans to
OL,15,Flegislate to modernise taxi and
OL,16,Fprivate hire vehicle licensing.
